workflow.name: lemlist <> GPT-3: Supercharge your sales workflows
workflow.description:
Use GPT-3 to classify email responses in lemlist.

And automate:

- Slack alerts when a lead is interested
- the creation of tasks when a lead is OOO
- unsubscription of leads when they request it

parameters.prompt:
=The following is a list of emails and the categories they fall into:
Categories=["interested", "Out of office", "unsubscribe", "other"]

Interested is when the reply is positive."
